{
  "page": "Corpse Lake",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Corpse_Lake.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ed/Corpse_Lake.jpg/350px-Corpse_Lake.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"232\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/e/ed/Corpse_Lake.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Corpse_Lake.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>© Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Corpse Lake</b> is a lake on the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>. It is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Corpse_Lake\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Corpse Lake\">House Goodbrother of Corpse Lake</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corpse_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corpse_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Greydon_Goodbrother\" title=\"Greydon Goodbrother\">Greydon Goodbrother</a> is sent by his father Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gorold_Goodbrother\" title=\"Gorold Goodbrother\">Gorold Goodbrother</a> to inform their cousins at <a href=\"/index.php/Downdelving\" title=\"Downdelving\">Downdelving</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Crow_Spike_Keep\" title=\"Crow Spike Keep\">Crow Spike Keep</a> and Corpse Lake of King <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a>'s death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corpse_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, The Prophet.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Template:Region Iron Islands\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;backgrou